---

<section
  class="hero-section relative h-[50vh] flex items-center justify-center"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
    <!-- Main Headline - LCP Optimized -->
    <h1
      class="hero-title font-instrument-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4 leading-tight font-normal"
    >
      Free SEO Checklist 2025 - Complete AI SEO Guide
    </h1>

    <!-- Subheadline - Critical Content -->
    <p
      class="hero-subtitle font-geist text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-normal mb-6"
    >
      Learn how to improve SEO rankings with our comprehensive checklist. 47+
      actionable steps covering keyword research, technical SEO, AI tools, and
      proven strategies to boost organic traffic.
    </p>

    <!-- Keywords - Lazy Loaded -->
    <div
      class="hero-keywords font-geist text-xs text-gray-500 max-w-xl mx-auto"
      style="content-visibility: auto; contain-intrinsic-size: 0 60px;"
    >
      <p class="mb-2">
        <strong class="text-gray-700">What you'll learn:</strong><br />Free SEO
        audit • AI SEO tools • How to do SEO • Keyword research • Technical SEO
        optimization • Local SEO • Content strategy • Link building • Page speed
        optimization
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Ultra-Optimized Hero Performance */
  .hero-section {
    contain: layout style paint;
    will-change: auto;
    transform: translateZ(0);
    backface-visibility: hidden;
  }

  .hero-title {
    text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;
    contain: layout style;
    font-synthesis: none;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    text-rendering: optimizeSpeed;
    contain: layout style;
    visibility: visible;
    font-synthesis: none;
  }

  .hero-keywords {
    contain: layout style;
    content-visibility: auto;
    contain-intrinsic-size: 0 60px;
  }
</style>
